imagenes.descripcion: The Drillpro 600mm China Woodworking Line Scriber T-Ruler is a useful tool for marking and measuring in woodworking. Its aluminum alloy construction ensures durability, while the cross rule marking gauge with 1mm holes helps with accurate measurements. It is a great tool for both professional carpenters and do-it-yourselfers.

VEIKO Aluminum Alloy 300mm Angle Positioning T Square Posi Lock Chinese Ruler is an accurate measuring tool. It features an adjustable nut design to change the angle of the ruler. The user simply presses the head to the desired angle. Both edges of the blade are laser engraved. The thin, satin aluminum alloy blade is easy to read and ideal for drawing parallel and angled lines.

Multi-angle China Ruler: Allows drawing angular lines at 45, 90, and 135 degrees. Drilling Ruler: Has specially designed holes for precise drawing of different lines. High-Quality Subtlety Ruler: Made of high-quality aluminum alloy, wear-resistant and corrosion-resistant. Precise Woodworking Ruler: Has clear and precise scale in inches and metrics. T Track Ruler for Vertical Measurement: Marked with depth measurement units for vertical measurements.

The China Mohoo Steel Ruler is a versatile tool for carpentry that allows for easy drawing of angular lines. It features specially designed holes for precise line drawing. Made of steel, it's wear-resistant and corrosion-resistant. It has clear scales in inches and metrics, and depth measurement units for vertical measurements.

The AIRAJ digital caliper is a stainless steel Vernier tool with a range of 0-300mm and an accuracy of +/-0.02mm. It features an LCD display, can measure in four directions, and is ideal for industrial and automotive applications. The package includes a digital caliper, a mini screwdriver, and instructions.

The Center Scribe Measuring Tool is a woodworking line gauge with a 45/90 degree right angle meter. Made of aluminum alloy, it is sturdy and durable, and allows for finding the center of round or square wood blocks. It is adjustable and useful for tracing at 45° and 90° in the manufacture of furniture and cabinets. It is suitable for carpenters, engineers, draftsmen, etc.

The Electronic Digital Goniometer Protractor is a stainless steel woodworking measuring tool with a range of 0-300mm / 0-360 degrees. It combines a ruler and a protractor in a 2-in-1 design, has a large LCD display, and a strong blade lock. It is perfect for DIY, engineering, woodworking, and home use.

The China Red Aluminum Alloy Miter Triangle Ruler 45°/90° is a durable and comfortable woodworking measurement tool. It has a thick ruler design for stability and accuracy, and is suitable for precise and general measurement jobs. It can be converted into two normal triangles by removing two screws, and is easy to use for marking 45/90 degree right and left angles.

The 1pc Steel Ruler Positioning Block is a high-precision woodworking tool for marking lines. It's made of durable materials and provides accurate measurements. It features a 90° angle for precise alignment and positioning, and can be used with a steel ruler, making it a versatile addition to any woodworking toolkit.

The Laser Digital China Protractor Inclinometer is a rechargeable measurement tool for determining angles and levels. It has a portable design, a high-definition non-angular lens, and a wide field of view. It features a magnetic design for installation on metal surfaces and can perform angle or tilt measurements in 4 directions.

The China Measuring Gauge Profile Scribing Ruler with Lock is an adjustable precise measurement tool for irregular radians. It's made of high-quality metal and ABS plastic, and the rollers use stainless steel bearings. This tool is useful for drawing irregular and complex objects, and can be locked and fixed after each adjustment to ensure accuracy.

The 1M 2M 10-parts Folding Carpenters Ruler is a lightweight and compact measuring stick designed for woodworking. It can slide and fold up, making it easy to carry and store. This ruler is perfect for carpenters who need a reliable and portable tool for their measuring needs.

The China Protractor Multi Angle Ruler Template is a 4-fold angle measuring tool ideal for measuring angles on bricks, tiles, wood, and corners. It's a foldable ruler, easy to store and carry. This tool is excellent for profiling a cut and is suitable for various applications. It's made of high-quality materials, ensuring durability and longevity.

A metal sheet thickness gauge is a tool used in welding to inspect the thickness of metal sheets. It’s made of stainless steel, is portable, and often includes a wire gauge to determine the wire diameter.

A professional miter saw protractor is a precision tool used in woodworking to measure angles with laser-engraved scales. It's typically 7 inches in size and is used to find precise angles for cutting corners.
A woodworking dovetail marker is a tool made of aluminum alloy used to mark dovetail joints in woodworking projects. It often comes with a 1:5 and 1:8 scale for different types of dovetail joints.

A multifunction caliper pen is a unique tool that combines the functionality of a vernier caliper with a gel ink pen. The pen, which can write in blue and black ink, has a built-in vernier caliper for taking quick measurements.

These cups come in 250 ml, 500 ml and 1000 ml sizes. They are made of pvc and have scales to measure liquids accurately. These utensils are essential in any type of work that requires measuring liquids, where accurate measurements are crucial.

China brake vernier caliper 0-60mm is a tool used to measure the thickness of brake discs. It is a crucial tool in automotive repair and maintenance, allowing mechanics to accurately measure the wear of brake discs.

Chinese dowel caliper for carpentry. This tool is used in carpentry to measure tenons very accurately. It often comes with metric and imperial scales and is typically used with a saw table machine. This tool is essential for ensuring accurate measurements on woodworking projects.

Fluorescent steel tape measure with self-locking fastener. These tape measures are usually available in 3 or 5 meter lengths. They are manufactured from high precision thick carbon steel for durability and accuracy. The measuring tapes usually incorporate a display for easy reading.

Wnew 3-in-1 Chinese dowel jig. Woodworking tool that serves as a hole punch, drill guide and positioning hole opener. It is designed to assist with the creation of dowel holes in do-it-yourself woodworking projects. The 3-in-1 refers to its multifunctional use.

DOCTORWOOD is a red aluminum Chinese jig for placing hardware in drawers, useful in carpentry. It works with metric and inch measurements, and includes 4mm and 5mm drilling guides. Its aluminum alloy construction ensures durability.

The China Drillpro Upgrade Aluminium Alloy 90 Degree 120x120mm is a precision carpentry clamping square with built-in measuring ruler. This L-shaped tool is useful for positioning and measuring right angles. It is made of aluminum alloy for durability.
